EVPN Broadcast, Unknown Unicast, or
Multicast (BUM) Using Bit Index Explicit
Replication (BIER)
2024", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC9624.html", target="_top", tooltip="This document specifies protocols and procedures for forwarding Broadcast, Unknown Unicast, or Multicast (BUM) traffic of Ethernet VPNs (EVPNs) using Bit Index Explicit Replication (BIER)."];
